    "description": "<div style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif;font-size:16px;line-height:1.6;color:#222;max-width:800px;margin:0 auto\" vocab=\"https://schema.org/\" typeof=\"Product\">\n  <div style=\"display:none\"><span property=\"description\">Spectra Cord by ASR Outdoor is a lightweight cord made from fiber&#039;s who&#039;s strength and versatility make it an ideal solution for virtually every rope and cordage requirement. One of the world’s strongest and lightest fibers, pound-for-pound, it is fifteen times stronger than steel. This Sleeved Spectra has a 325 lb. tensile strength. Constructed of Spectra 1000 base with a polyester braided sleeve for UV and abrasion resistance. Heat set and stretched. Great for Sports and Outdoors applications.</span></div>\n  <div style=\"background:#f5f5f5;padding:12px 15px;border:1px solid #e5e5e5;margin:0 0 16px\">\n    <div style=\"font-size:18px;font-weight:bold;margin-bottom:6px\">Deals Only Web Store</div>\n    <div style=\"font-size:13px\">\n      <a href=\"https://www.ebay.com/str/dealsonlywebstore\" style=\"text-decoration:none;color:#333\">Our Store</a>\n    </div>\n  </div>\n  <h2 style=\"font-size:22px;margin:0 0 12px\">ASR Outdoor Cord 325lb Survival Tactical Polyester Sleeved Rope 25ft 100ft 500ft</h2>\n  <p>Spectra Cord by ASR Outdoor is a lightweight cord made from fiber&#039;s who&#039;s strength and versatility make it an ideal solution for virtually every rope and cordage requirement. One of the world’s strongest and lightest fibers, pound-for-pound, it is fifteen times stronger than steel. This Sleeved Spectra has a 325 lb. tensile strength.</p>\n  <h3 style=\"font-size:18px;margin:18px 0 8px\">Key Features</h3>\n  <ul style=\"padding-left:20px;margin:0 0 16px\">\n    <li>Great for Sports and Outdoors or Emergency and Survival applications</li>\n    <li><strong>Core Material:</strong> Spectra 1000 | Sleeving: Braided Polyester</li>\n    <li><strong>Tensile Strength:</strong> 325 lbs | Diameter: (0.073 in) - (1.85 mm)</li>\n    <li>High strength-to-size ratio, allowing for lighter weight ropes that are easier to handle and maneuver</li>\n    <li>Superior chemical resistance, increased abrasion resistance and excellent flex fatigue, meaning products last longer and maintenance costs are lower</li>\n  </ul>\n  <p style=\"text-align:center;margin:0 0 16px\"><img src=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/DOWS_products/1000x1000/camping_outdoors/cord/Bspc060_spectra_blk_wrap_outdoor.jpg\" alt=\"Spectra Cord by ASR Outdoor is a lightweight cord made from fiber&#039;s who&#039;s strength and versatility make it an ideal solution for virtually every rope\" style=\"max-width:100%;width:600px;height:auto\"></p>\n  <h3 style=\"font-size:18px;margin:18px 0 8px\">Product Specifications</h3>\n  <ul style=\"padding-left:20px;margin:0 0 16px\">\n    <li><strong>MPN:</strong> 17678</li>\n    <li><strong>UPC:</strong> 695296080487</li>\n  </ul>\n  <p>Constructed of Spectra 1000 base with a polyester braided sleeve for UV and abrasion resistance. Heat set and stretched.</p>\n  <p>Great for Sports and Outdoors applications.</p>\n  <p style=\"text-align:center;margin:16px 0 0\"><img src=\"https://s3.us-east-1.amazonaws.com/DOWS_photobucket/Shopify_Prop65graphic.jpg\" alt=\"California Proposition 65 warning\" style=\"display:block;margin-left:auto;margin-right:auto\" height=\"78\" width=\"273\"></p>\n  <p style=\"margin:18px 0 0;padding-top:12px;border-top:1px solid #e5e5e5;font-size:13px;color:#777;text-align:center\">&copy; 2026 Deals Only Web Store</p>\n</div>",
    "short_description": "Spectra Cord by ASR Outdoor is a lightweight cord made from fiber's who's strength and versatility make it an ideal solution for virtually every rope and cordage requirement. One of the world’s strongest and lightest fibers, pound-for-pound, it is fifteen times stronger than steel. This Sleeved Spectra has a 325 lb. tensile strength. Constructed of Spectra 1000 base with a polyester braided sleeve for UV and abrasion resistance. Heat set and stretched. Great for Sports and Outdoors applications.",
